column4: Welcome, you are now talking to an AI doctor. As I am part of a scientific experiment, I would appreciate it if you could take the time to answer a super short questionnaire at the end of the interview. Tap Speak to ask your question and then tap Send to submit it to me.
what is 20,000 to the power of 3
I apologize, but I am unable to answer that question. My specialty is in medicine, not mathematics. If you have any medical questions, I would be happy to help.

The best medicine often depends on the particular medical condition and individual patient. I suggest discussing with a healthcare professional what the best treatment option is for your particular situation.
Hello! How may I be of assistance?
do you like imagine dragons do you
I apologize, but I am unable to answer that question. My specialty is in medicine, not music. If you have any medical questions, I would be happy to help.

I cannot say I have a favorite medicine, as each medicine has its advantages and disadvantages. I would suggest discussing with a healthcare professional what the best treatment option is for your particular condition.
I am a digital doctor, and I specialize in answering medical questions.
